ed specific details from before exiting plan mode (like exact code snippets, error messages, or content you generated), read the full transcript at: /Users/gtrrz-victor/.claude/projects/-Users-gtrrz-victor-wks-cli-remove-auto-commit/09554965-e2ee-48ec-8c80-4d3382a45483.jsonl\"},\"uuid\":\"afbaca52-de96-4d1b-88fb-627b5b95abcd\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-23T04:20:33.191Z\",\"planContent\":\"# Add Debug Timing Logs to Git Hooks\\n\\n## Context\\n\\nPerformance testing of the prepare-commit-msg hook. Need visibility into how long the main hook methods take.\\n\\n## Approach\\n\\nAdd `logging.LogDuration` calls at the top of each main hook method using `defer`, so the total time of each method is logged at `DEBUG` level.\\n\\n## Files to Modify\\n\\n### 1. `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go`\\n\\nAdd `defer logging.LogDuration(...)` at the top of:\\n- `PrepareCommitMsg()` (line 234)\\n- `handleAmendCommitMsg()` (line 393)\\n- `CommitMsg()` (line 125)\\n- `PostCommit()` (line 602)\\n\\n## Pattern\\n\\n```go\\nfunc (s *ManualCommitStrategy) PrepareCommitMsg(...) error {\\n    start := time.Now()\\n    defer logging.LogDuration(logCtx, slog.LevelDebug, \\\"PrepareCommitMsg total\\\", start)\\n    // ... rest unchanged\\n}\\n```\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n1. Set `ENTIRE_LOG_LEVEL=DEBUG`\\n2. Make a commit in a repo with an active session\\n3. Check `.entire/logs/entire.log` for timing entries\\n4. `mise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci`\\n\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"afbaca52-de96-4d1b-88fb-627b5b95abcd\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/gtrrz-victor/wks/cli/remove-auto-commit\",\"sessionId\":\"d1edaaf5-0e56-4080-8ccf-d4691be6ffc9\",\"version\":\"2.1.50\",\"gitBranch\":\"gtrrz-victor/pre-commit-performance\",\"slug\":\"enchanted-weaving-newt\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_015AEKGZK8T942GqqmRUgPJW\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Let me st