wBenchRepo_Large`: Creates repo with 50 files × 500 lines\\n- `BenchmarkSeedShadowBranch`: Seeds 1/5/10 checkpoints on shadow branch\\n- `BenchmarkSeedMetadataBranch`: Seeds 1/5/10 checkpoints on metadata branch\\n- `BenchmarkGenerateTranscript`: Tests transcript generation at various scales\\n- `BenchmarkCreateSessionState`: Tests session state file writing\\n\\n### 2. Integration Test Patterns (`cmd/entire/cli/integration_test/`)\\n\\n**Main Helper: `TestEnv`**\\n- Manages isolated test repository and project directories\\n- Does NOT change working directory (allows parallel test execution)\\n- Uses temp directories for repo, Claude project dir, Gemini project dir, OpenCode project dir\\n\\n**Key Setup Methods**:\\n\\n```go\\n// Environment creation\\nNewTestEnv(t *testing.T) *TestEnv\\nNewRepoEnv(t *testing.T, strategy string) *TestEnv              // Git repo + Entire\\nNewRepoWithCommit(t *testing.T, strategy string) *TestEnv       // + initial commit\\nNewFeatureBranchEnv(t *testing.T, strategyName string) *TestEnv // + feature branch\\n\\n// Initialization\\nInitRepo()                                    // Initialize git repo\\nInitEntire(strategyName string)               // Create .entire/settings.json\\nInitEntireWithOptions(strategyName string, options map[string]any)\\nInitEntireWithAgent(strategyName string, agent agent.AgentName)\\nInitEntireWithAgentAndOptions(...)\\n```\\n\\n**Parameterized Test Helpers**:\\n\\n```go\\nRunForAllStrategies(t *testing.T, testFn func(t *testing.T, env *TestEnv, strategyName string))\\nRunForAllStrategiesWithRepoEnv(...)  // Uses NewRepoWithCommit\\nRunForAllStrategiesWithBasicEnv(...) // Uses NewRepoEnv (no commits)\\nRunForStrategiesSequential(t *testing.T, strategies []string, testFn func(t *testing.T, strategyName string))\\nAllStrategies() []string             // Returns [\\\"auto-commit\\\", \\\"manual-commit\\\"]\\n```\\n\\n**File Operations**:\\n\\n```go\\nWriteFile(path, content string)\\nReadFile(path string) s