teTemporary` with empty MetadataDir (which is what `carryForwardToNewShadowBranch` does).\\n\\n3. For Scenario 3 (no shadow branch, live transcript): Don't create any shadow branch. Write a live transcript file to disk using `WriteTranscriptFile`. Set session phase to ACTIVE.\\n\\nFor all scenarios, we need staged files that overlap with the session's files to trigger the full code path.\\n\\n## Design Requirements\\n\\n- Create a single benchmark file, e.g. `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/prepare_commit_msg_bench_test.go`\\n- Each scenario should be a sub-benchmark with varying parameters (transcript size, number of files)\\n- The benchmark should call the actual `PrepareCommitMsg` method (or at minimum `sessionHasNewContent`)\\n- Use `b.ResetTimer()` after setup\\n- Follow existing Go benchmark patterns in the codebase\\n\\nPlease design the implementation plan including the file structure, setup for each scenario, and what exactly gets benchmarked.\",\"agentId\":\"a52a53d9051067ba3\"},\"toolUseID\":\"agent_msg_01AHsMcmZ21hbgnscoskufUo\",\"parentToolUseID\":\"toolu_01PAzSjrZPJhGZKgqgzRn4rP\",\"uuid\":\"ea84e1d0-2eda-4a06-a8cc-df866dbeba47\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-23T05:25:18.551Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"ea84e1d0-2eda-4a06-a8cc-df866dbeba47\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/gtrrz-victor/wks/cli/remove-auto-commit\",\"sessionId\":\"d1edaaf5-0e56-4080-8ccf-d4691be6ffc9\",\"version\":\"2.1.50\",\"gitBranch\":\"gtrrz-victor/pre-commit-performance\",\"slug\":\"enchanted-weaving-newt\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"message\":{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-23T05:25:19.276Z\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_012M9TkSByg5hUsFRXduUBoP\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01WRvFMs8BN6cYy3vuJ6DPqs\",\"name\":\"Grep\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"func.*ShadowBranchNameForCommit\",\"path\":\"/Users/gtrrz-victor/wks/cli/remove-auto-commit/cmd/entire/cli/che